<div class="content"><nav class="breadcrumb" aria-label="Breadcrumb"><a href="/">Home</a> › <a href="/moving/">Moving</a> › Moving Truck Wraps Chicago</nav><h1>Moving Truck Wraps in Chicago</h1><p class="lead speakable">Chicago Fleet Wraps designs and installs professional moving truck wraps for moving companies across Chicago and Chicagoland. Moving trucks are the largest mobile billboards on the road — a single wrapped 26-ft box truck generates 50,000–70,000 daily impressions driving through residential neighborhoods during peak moving season. We use Avery Dennison MPI 1105 and 3M IJ180-CV3 cast vinyl with a 2-year workmanship warranty. Free fleet pickup throughout Chicagoland.</p><div class="cta-bar"><a href="/estimate/" class="btn btn-primary">Get a Moving Truck Wrap Quote →</a><a href="tel:+13125971286" class="btn" style="border-color:var(--gold);color:var(--gold)">📞 Call Now</a></div><div class="trust"><span>📅 <strong>24+ Years</strong> Experience</span><span>🏆 <strong>9,400+</strong> Vehicles Wrapped</span><span>✅ <strong>Avery & 3M</strong> Certified</span><span>📦 <strong>300+</strong> Moving Fleets Branded</span><span>🚐 <strong>Free Pickup</strong></span></div><img src="/images/windy_city_box_truck.webp" alt="Windy City moving truck wrap — box truck graphics by Chicago Fleet Wraps" style="width:100%;border-radius:8px;margin:0 0 24px" loading="lazy"><h2>Why Moving Companies Need Truck Wraps</h2><p class="body-text">Moving trucks spend all day in residential neighborhoods — the exact places where future customers live. A professionally wrapped moving truck parked in a driveway for 4–8 hours during a move generates hundreds of close-range impressions from neighbors, dog walkers, and passing cars. Chicago has over 100,000 residential moves per year, and a branded truck builds instant recognition and trust.</p><p class="body-text">Unlike digital ads that disappear when you stop paying, a wrapped moving truck works 24/7 — on the highway, at storage facilities, and parked at your yard. At $0.04 CPM, vehicle wraps deliver the lowest cost-per-impression of any advertising medium. Many moving companies report that a single wrapped truck generates 3–5 direct leads per week.</p><h2>Moving Vehicle Types We Wrap</h2><ul class="services"><li><strong>Box Trucks 16 ft</strong> — Ideal for apartment and small home moves. Full wraps from $5,000.</li><li><strong>Box Trucks 20 ft</strong> — Mid-size residential moves. Full wraps from $6,600.</li><li><strong>Box Trucks 24–26 ft</strong> — Large home and commercial moves. Full wraps from $8,500–$10,900.</li><li><strong>Cargo Vans</strong> — Ford Transit, Ram ProMaster, Chevy Express for small moves and delivery. $2,800–$4,500.</li><li><strong>Sprinter Vans</strong> — High-roof sprinters for specialty moving services. $3,500–$5,200.</li><li><strong>Pickup Trucks & Trailers</strong> — Support vehicles and enclosed trailers. $1,800–$4,200.</li></ul><h2>Moving Truck Wrap Pricing</h2><ul class="services"><li><strong>16 ft Box Truck Full Wrap</strong> — $5,000–$6,500</li><li><strong>20 ft Box Truck Full Wrap</strong> — $6,600–$8,000</li><li><strong>24–26 ft Box Truck Full Wrap</strong> — $8,500–$10,900</li><li><strong>Cargo Van Full Wrap</strong> — $2,800–$4,500</li><li><strong>Partial Wrap / Lettering</strong> — $1,200–$3,000</li><li><strong>Fleet Discounts</strong> — 5% off 3–4 vehicles, 10% off 5–9, 15% off 10+</li></ul><p class="body-text">All moving truck wraps are <strong>100% tax deductible</strong> under IRS Section 179 as a business advertising expense.</p>
