<h2>Moving Truck Wrap Design Best Practices</h2><p class="body-text">The most effective moving truck wraps feature <strong>company name</strong> visible from 200+ feet (box truck sides are massive canvases), a <strong>phone number</strong> in the largest font possible, your <strong>website and Google review rating</strong>, and 2–3 key service areas. Include your license/DOT numbers for credibility. Bold, clean designs with high contrast outperform cluttered layouts — your truck is moving at speed and needs to communicate in seconds. <a href="/fleet-wraps-chicago/" style="color:var(--gold)">Learn about our fleet branding process →</a></p><h2>Frequently Asked Questions</h2><div class="faq-item"><h3>How much does a moving truck wrap cost in Chicago?</h3><p>Moving truck wraps range from $5,000–$10,900 for box trucks (16–26 ft). Cargo van wraps start at $2,800–$4,500. Fleet discounts of 5–15% apply for 3+ vehicles.</p></div><div class="faq-item"><h3>How long does a moving truck wrap last?</h3><p>Premium cast vinyl wraps are rated for 5–7 years. Quality installation with Avery Dennison or 3M materials ensures durability through heavy daily use, loading/unloading, and highway driving.</p></div><div class="faq-item"><h3>Can you wrap a fleet of moving trucks?</h3><p>Absolutely. We specialize in fleet rollouts and can wrap multiple trucks on a phased schedule to minimize downtime. Fleet discounts apply for 3+ vehicles.</p></div><div class="faq-item"><h3>Do moving truck wraps protect the truck body?</h3><p>Yes. Vinyl wraps act as a protective layer against minor scratches, stone chips, and UV fading. When removed, the original paint underneath is preserved.</p></div><div class="cta-bar"><a href="/estimate/" class="btn btn-primary">Get Your Moving Truck Wrap Quote →</a><a href="tel:+13125971286" class="btn" style="border-color:var(--gold);color:var(--gold)">📞 (312) 597-1286</a></div></div>